					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I'm glad to see someone finally building this.<br /><br />The next question is how to emulate this. The obvious signal for this would be an NES 2.0 header with zero CHR ROM and zero CHR RAM, but that leaves what sort of mirroring to choose. Can't A12 already do everything A13 does, plus the ability to enable rendering late or disable it early to add a few more tiles?</div>

